select * from `conges` inner join `conges_etats_conge` on `etat_conge_id` = `conges_etats_conge`.`id` inner join `conges_types_conge` on `type_conge_id` = `conges_types_conge`.`id` inner join `conges_frequences_solde` on `conges_types_conge`.`frequence_solde_id` = `conges_frequences_solde`.`id` inner join `employes` on `employe_id` = `employes`.`id` where `employe_id` = 4 limit 100
